div.p: Commutative Property: a x b = b x a
Associative Property: (a x b) x c = a x (b x c)
Multiplication Property of Zero: a x 0 = 0
Distributive Property: a x (b + c) = (a x b) + (a x c)

ul.li: Demonstrates: Identity Property and Multiplication Property of Zero
Identity: Multiplying by 1 leaves the number unchanged.
